name: Delve Yoiul Calendar
description: This unorthodox and digitally enhanced Yoiul calendar hides, behind each of its 24 door progams, a reminder of what can happen if extensive mining operations are conducted during important events like a 'State of the Alliance' speech. Activating the doors will reveal beautifully animated, detailed images of destructions of 19 Rorquals, two Supercarriers, two Mining Barges and one Battleship.
